  "content": "<p>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.4TX2Q1MaWt1B8298]{(Index) Items}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.j1KZwBRf9pU1Dg2C]{6.0. Equipment}</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.IcxBfkvPZ6hdWRuV]{6.0.3. Armor}\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.DWU53DrpWkZoEyfe]{6.0.3.1. Masterwork Armor}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.ukz9B0kwM0KtLvRf]{6.0.3.2. Armor for Unusual Creatures}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.IHv2CuhMxrDUDNuf]{6.0.3.3. Getting Into and Out of Armor}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>Source PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 153</p>\n<p>Armor and shields for unusually big creatures, unusually little creatures, and nonhumanoid creatures (such as horses) have different costs and weights from those given on Table 6&ndash;6. Refer to the appropriate line on Table 6&ndash;8 and apply the multipliers to cost and weight for the armor type in question.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Table 6-8: Armor for Unusual Creatures</h2>\n<table style=\"width: 72.9036%;\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\" scope=\"col\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 28.0116%;\" colspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\">Humanoid</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 33.2366%;\" colspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\">Nonhumanoid</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\" scope=\"col\">Size</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 11.4659%;\" scope=\"col\">Cost</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 16.5457%;\" scope=\"col\">Weight</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 12.627%;\" scope=\"col\">Cost</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 20.6096%;\" scope=\"col\">Weight</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\">Tiny or smaller*</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 11.4659%;\">&times;1/2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 16.5457%;\">&times;1/10</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 12.627%;\">&times;1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 20.6096%;\">&times;1/10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\">Small</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 11.4659%;\">&times;1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 16.5457%;\">&times;1/2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 12.627%;\">&times;2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 20.6096%;\">&times;1/2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\">Medium</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 11.4659%;\">&times;1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 16.5457%;\">&times;1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 12.627%;\">&times;2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 20.6096%;\">&times;1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\">Large</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 11.4659%;\">&times;2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 16.5457%;\">&times;2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 12.627%;\">&times;4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 20.6096%;\">&times;2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\">Huge</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 11.4659%;\">&times;4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 16.5457%;\">&times;5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 12.627%;\">&times;8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 20.6096%;\">&times;5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\">Gargantuan</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 11.4659%;\">&times;8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 16.5457%;\">&times;8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 12.627%;\">&times;16</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 20.6096%;\">&times;8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 37.5907%;\">Colossal</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 11.4659%;\">&times;16</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 16.5457%;\">&times;12</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 12.627%;\">&times;32</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 20.6096%;\">&times;12</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>*Divide armor bonus by 2.</p>"
